---
title: Cashflow — Consultar saldo diário (GET /consolidation/api/v1/balances/{merchantId}/daily)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Merchant as Merchant
    participant GW as Gateway (YARP)
    participant API as Consolidation.Api
    participant CACHE as Redis
    participant MGO as MongoDB
    participant POLLY as Polly pipeline<br/>(mongo-read)

    Merchant->>+GW: GET /consolidation/api/v1/balances/{merchantId}/daily?date=2026-05-14<br/>Bearer JWT
    GW->>GW: Valida JWT (JWKS cache)
    GW->>GW: Rate-limit balance-read-policy<br/>(120/s/merchant — 2× NFR)
    GW->>+API: Proxy + X-Correlation-Id + traceparent
    API->>API: BalancesEndpoints — RequireMerchant policy
    API->>API: Resource-based check<br/>(merchantId path == claim merchantId)
    API->>API: GetDailyBalanceQuery → Handler

    rect rgb(245, 250, 245)
    note over API,CACHE: Cache aside (TTL 60s)
        API->>+CACHE: GET daily_balance:{merchantId}:{date}
        alt cache HIT (≥95% das req em estado estacionário)
            CACHE-->>-API: payload JSON serializado
            API-->>GW: 200 OK<br/>cache: {hit: true, ageSeconds: 12}
            GW-->>Merchant: 200 OK
        else cache MISS
            CACHE-->>API: nil
            API->>+CACHE: SET miss_lock:... NX EX 5
            alt won lock (1 caller por janela)
                CACHE-->>-API: OK (lock acquired)
                rect rgb(252, 245, 245)
                note over API,POLLY: Polly resilience pipeline
                    API->>+POLLY: ExecuteAsync
                    POLLY->>+MGO: db.daily_balance.findOne({merchantId, date})
                    MGO-->>-POLLY: doc | null
                    POLLY-->>-API: result (Timeout 2s / CB / Retry exp 3x)
                end
                API->>CACHE: SET daily_balance:... EX 60
                API->>CACHE: DEL miss_lock:...
                API-->>GW: 200 OK<br/>cache: {hit: false, ageSeconds: 0}
                GW-->>Merchant: 200 OK
            else lost lock (callers concorrentes)
                CACHE-->>API: nil (key already exists)
                note over API: Task.Delay(100ms)
                API->>+CACHE: GET daily_balance:... (relê)
                alt cache populated by winner
                    CACHE-->>-API: payload
                    API-->>GW: 200 OK<br/>cache: {hit: true}
                    GW-->>Merchant: 200 OK
                else still empty (winner crashed?)
                    note over API: fallback: lê Mongo direto<br/>(proteção contra deadlock por crash do winner)
                    API->>MGO: findOne (sem lock)
                    MGO-->>API: doc
                    API-->>GW: 200 OK
                    GW-->>Merchant: 200 OK
                end
            end
        end
    end

    Note over Merchant,MGO: NFR-P-02 P95 cache hit under 200ms (real 53ms). Aggregate under 500ms.
